OL,3,CEllie Goulding among thousands calling
OL,4,Cfor national inquiry into baby's death
OL,6,FSinger Ellie Goulding and Carrie
OL,7,FJohnson, the wife of former prime
OL,8,Fminister Boris Johnson, have signed a
OL,9,Fpetition calling for a national
OL,10,Finquiry into the death of Preston
OL,11,FDavey, which has passed 100,000
OL,12,Fsignatures.
OL,14,FThe 13-month old boy was sexually
OL,15,Fabused and murdered by his adoptive
OL,16,Ffather, who was a former high school
OL,17,Fteacher.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
