OL,3,CEllie Goulding among thousands calling
OL,4,Cfor national inquiry into baby's death
OL,6,FHe was given a whole life term and
OL,7,Ftold he will never be eligible for
OL,8,Fparole. His partner John McGowan-
OL,9,FFazakerley, 32, was jailed for 25
OL,10,Fyears for allowing Varley's treatment
OL,11,Fof the child and taking part in the
OL,12,Fsexual abuse.
OL,14,FIn the wake of the sentencing, a
OL,15,Fpetition titled: "Preston Davey
OL,16,Fdeserved better. Demand a national
OL,17,Finquiry".
OL,26,@wD@ROUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
