OL,3,CEllie Goulding among thousands calling
OL,4,Cfor national inquiry into baby's death
OL,6,FThe petition, backed by Blackpool
OL,7,FSouth MP Chris Webb and Preston's
OL,8,Fbirth parents Sarah Davey and Gary
OL,9,FNolan, calls for "a national inquiry
OL,10,Finto the safeguarding failures that
OL,11,Fcost Preston his life".
OL,13,FLights singer Goulding, who is mother
OL,14,Fto two young children, and Johnson,
OL,15,Fwho shares four children with the
OL,16,Fformer prime minister, have added
OL,17,Ftheir names to the petition, which was
OL,18,Flaunched on 18 June.
OL,26,@qD@ROUsD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
