FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1782816485
OL,3,CEllie Goulding among thousands calling
OL,4,Cfor national inquiry into baby's death
OL,6,FShe committed to rolling out new
OL,7,Fsafeguards in the Children's Wellbeing
OL,8,Fand Schools Act 2026 by March, telling
OL,9,FMPs: "Our thoughts must be with all of
OL,10,Fthose who loved and knew Preston, and
OL,11,Fit is right that the evil abusers that
OL,12,Fcommitted these sickening and shocking
OL,13,Fcrimes are now behind bars.
OL,26,@qD@FOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1782816485
OL,3,CEllie Goulding among thousands calling
OL,4,Cfor national inquiry into baby's death
OL,6,F"The House can be assured that we take
OL,7,Fthis extremely seriously, it is why I
OL,8,Fhave asked for independent experts to
OL,9,Flook at Oldham Council, Blackpool
OL,10,FTeaching Hospitals NHS Trust and the
OL,11,Fregional adoption agency to look
OL,12,Fcarefully at all of the issues and
OL,13,Fconcerns that have been raised through
OL,14,Fthis process.
OL,16,F"The child safeguard practice review
OL,17,Fis commencing, led by the local
OL,18,Fsafeguarding partnership with the
OL,19,Fnational child safeguarding practice
OL,20,Freview, working closely to make sure
OL,21,Fit is of the highest quality."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
