PN,36507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1782816485
OL,3,CEllie Goulding among thousands calling
OL,4,Cfor national inquiry into baby's death
OL,6,FMs Phillipson added: "It is an urgent
OL,7,Fpriority for this incoming Government
OL,8,Fto update legislation to make sure we
OL,9,Fdo everything within our power to keep
OL,10,Fchildren safe."I am glad that justice
OL,11,Fhas been served.
OL,13,F"We can't bring Preston back, but we
OL,14,Fcan make sure that we do everything
OL,15,Fwithin our power to stop this
OL,16,Fhappening to other children in future."
OL,26,@nD@VOUrD@OOUuD@AOUxD@gO]
